o Monteiro]] | title = [[Autosport]]<br />Rookie of the Year | after = [[Sebastian Vettel]]| years =2006\u20132007}}\n{{Succession box| title=[[Hawthorn Memorial Trophy]] | before= [[Jenson Button]] | after= [[Jenson Button]]| years=2007\u20132008}}\n{{succession box | before = [[Stirling Moss]] | title = [[Segrave Trophy]] | after =[[Allan McNish]]| years = 2007}}\n{{Succession box| before = [[Jenson Button]] | title = [[Autosport]]<br />British Competition Driver of the Year | after = [[Allan McNish]]| years = 2007}}\n{{Succession box| before = [[Fernando Alonso]] | title = [[Autosport]]<br />International Racing Driver Award | after = [[Jenson Button]]| years = 2007\u20132008}}\n{{Succession box| before = [[Am\u00e9lie Mauresmo]] | after = [[Rebecca Adlington]] | title = [[Laureus World Sports Award for Breakthrough of the Year|Laureus World Breakthrough of the Year]] | years = 2008}}\n{{Succession box|before= [[Sebastian Vettel]]|title=[[Lorenzo Bandini Trophy]]|years=2010|after= [[Nico Rosberg]]}}\n{{Succession box| title=[[Hawthorn Memorial Trophy]] | before= [[Jenson Button]] | after= [[Mark Webber]]| years=2012}}\n{{Succession box| before = [[Jenson Button]] | title = [[Autosport]]<br />British Competition Driver of the Year | after = [[Lando Norris]]| years = 2013\u20132018}}\n{{Succession box| title=[[Hawthorn Memorial Trophy]] | before= [[Mark Webber]] | after= Incumbent| years=2014\u20132019}}\n{{Succession box|before=[[Sebastian Vettel]]|title=[[DHL Fastest Lap Award]]|years={{F1|2014}}\u2013{{F1|2015}}|after=[[Nico Rosberg]]}}\n{{Succession box|before= [[Sebastian Vettel]]|title=[[Autosport]]<br />International Racing Driver Award|after=[[Nico Rosberg]]|years=2014\u20132015}}\n{{Succession box|before = [[Andy Murray]]| after = [[Andy Murray]]| title = [[BBC Sports Personality of the Year Award|BBC Sports Personality of the Year]]| years = [[2014 BBC Sports Personality of the Year Award|2014]]}}\n{{s-bef|before = [[Robert Kubica]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[FIA Prize Giving Ceremony#Personality of the Year|FIA Personality of the Year]]|years=2014}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Max Verstappen]]}}\n{{Succession box|before= [[Nico Rosberg]]|title=[[FIA Pole Trophy]]|years={{F1|2015}}\u2013{{F1|2016}}\u2013{{F1|2017}}\u2013{{F1|2018}}|after=[[Charles Leclerc]]}}\n{{Succession box|before=[[Nico Rosberg]]|title=[[DHL Fastest Lap Award]]|years={{F1|2017}}|after=[[Valtteri Bottas]]}}\n{{Succession box|before= [[Nico Rosberg]]|title=[[Autosport]]<br />International Racing Driver Award|after=Incumbent|years=2017\u20132019}}\n{{Succession box|before=[[Valtteri Bottas]]|title=[[DHL Fastest Lap Award]]|years={{F1|2019}}|after=Incumbent}}\n{{S-ach|rec}}\n{{s-bef|before = [[Juan Manuel Fangio]]<br>and<br>[[Giuseppe Farina]]<small><br>3 wins<br>([[1950 Formula One season|1950 season]])</small>}}\n{{s-ttl|title = [[List of Formula One driver records#Most wins in first championship season|Most wins in first Formula One season]]<br />4 wins|years = {{F1|2007}}<small>, tied with:</small><br />[[Jacques Villeneuve]] ({{F1|1996}})}}\n{{s-aft|after=Co-Incumbent}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Bruce McLaren]]<br><small>23 years, 5 days<br>([[1960 Formula One season|1960 season]])</small>}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Youngest Formula One<br>World Drivers' Championship runner-up|years=22 years, 287 days<br>([[2007 Formula One World Championship|2007 season]])}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Sebastian Vettel]]<br><small>22 years, 121 days<br>([[2009 Formula One World Championship|2009 season]])</small>}}\n{{Succession box|title=[[List of Formula One World Drivers' Champions#Youngest Drivers' Champion|Youngest Formula One<br />World Drivers' Champion]]| before = [[Fernando Alonso]]<small><br />24 years, 58 days<br />([[2005 Formula One World Championship|2005 season]])</small> | after = [[Sebastian Vettel]]<small><br />23 years, 134 days<br />([[2010 Formula One World Championship|2010 season]])</small> | years = 23 years, 300 days<br />([[2008 Formula One World Championship|2008 season]])}}\n{{su