/http://www.itv-f1.com/news_article.aspx?id=44730|archivedate=9 December 2008|url-status=dead|accessdate=5 September 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.autosport.com/awards/news/117071/international-racing-driver-hamilton|title=AUTOSPORT Awards 2014: Lewis Hamilton wins International Driver|magazine=Autosport|accessdate=5 September 2017}}</ref><ref name=\"auto14\">{{cite magazine|url=https://www.autosport.com/awards/news/122164/hamilton-takes-two-autosport-awards|title=Autosport Awards 2015: Lewis Hamilton wins two awards|magazine=Autosport|accessdate=5 September 2017}}</ref><ref name=\"auto15\">{{cite magazine|url=https://www.autosport.com/awards/news/133420/hamilton-secures-autosport-awards-double|title=Autosport Awards 2017 \u2013 Lewis Hamilton claims two awards|magazine=Autosport|accessdate=4 December 2017}}</ref><ref name=\"AA18\">{{cite news|url=https://www.autosport.com/awards/news/140464/hamilton-gets-another-autosport-awards-double|title=F1 champion Lewis Hamilton gets another Autosport Awards double|first=Jack|last=Cozens|work=[[Autosport]]|publisher=[[Motorsport Network]]|date=2 December 2018|accessdate=2 December 2018}}</ref>\n* [[Autosport Awards#British Competition Driver of the Year|Autosport British Competition Driver of the Year]]: 2007, 2013, 2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, 2018<ref name=\"Hamilton bags Awards hat-trick\" /><ref name=\"auto14\"/><ref name=\"auto15\"/><ref name=\"AA18\"/><ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.autosport.com/awards/news/111685/british-driver-lewis-hamilton|title=AUTOSPORT Awards: Lewis Hamilton wins British Competition Driver|magazine=Autosport|accessdate=5 September 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.autosport.com/awards/news/117070/british-driver-lewis-hamilton|title=AUTOSPORT Awards 2014: Lewis Hamilton wins British Driver|magazine=Autosport|accessdate=5 September 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.autosport.com/awards/news/127391/british-competition-driver-hamilton|title=Autosport 